{"tid":651860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[隊友] 南韓2022年前裁軍11萬人 未來還要把兵役縮短至18個月","createTime":"2018-05-03T12:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T13:05:18.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5362932bb07c1a91343a93fe0b9f129174beb0fa","tid":651860,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:03:29.000Z","msg":"南韓2022年前裁軍11萬人 未來還要把兵役縮短至18個月<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2414243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2414243&d=xEcxK8RUtCiVCfvhxqzm57%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=4c916f92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2414243&h=457aefc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2414243</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕南韓總統文在寅在競選期間曾拋出國防改革方案，南韓國防部也將於本月中旬向文在寅提交《國防改革2.0》方案，內容指出會將義務役役期從目前的21個月縮短至18個月，另外會將陸軍裁軍11萬。<br />\n<br />\n根據南韓《韓聯社》報導，南韓國防部針對役期做說明，表示將在未來2年6個月內逐漸縮短役期，力求在2020年11月把役期縮短至18個月。目前正在服兵役的南韓官兵也受惠於此正策政，有望提前退伍。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">過去南韓盧武鉉政府執政的2003年，南韓陸軍兵役期限從26個月縮短至24個月，2007年時更縮短至18個月；李明博執政時期的2011年，役期重新調整至21個月；朴槿惠政府曾計劃將役期縮短至18個月，但國防部方面表示有困難，因此沒有減少。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外，南韓國防部也將在2022年把兵力從61萬裁減至50萬，但裁軍範圍僅涉及陸軍，海軍、空軍兵力將保持目前人數。</span>據統計，南韓兵力規模截至去年底為陸軍48萬、海軍3.9萬、空軍6.3萬、海軍陸戰隊2.8萬。"},{"pid":"5b4cbedbaeb862380385179163e765a8426c9c6b","tid":651860,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"好快北韓統一朝鮮半島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164fe8c64fda2a674a2a72f79e6cb0c8359280fa","tid":651860,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b4cbedbaeb862380385179163e765a8426c9c6b","tid":651860,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"好快北韓統一朝鮮半島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f68e375b72e5231312f7896ea7ce7a18c4cd189","tid":651860,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:02:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c8d0d6ec073a5aacab76f350a78f37913641949","tid":651860,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"個撚個後生去晒做偶像實習生，打仗一齊扯甩個鼻當手榴彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}